            <abstract>
                <p><foreign xml:lang="gez">Qǝne</foreign> without type indication in the manuscript. It has eight lines, meaning
                    that it might be classified as a <foreign xml:lang="gez">mawaddǝs qǝne</foreign> according to
                    <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/C92MK42D"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Guidi1900Qene"/><title level="a">"Qenê" o inni abissini</title><title level="j">Atti della Reale Accademia dei Lincei, Rendiconti, Classe di scienze morale, storiche e filologiche</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Ignazio</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Guidi</t:surname></author><date>1900</date><biblScope unit="volume">Serie quinta, 9</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">463-510</biblScope></bibl>. 
                    It is attributed to <persName cert="high" corresp="SD" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14574GabraLeul">Gabra Lǝʿul</persName> 
                    in the manuscript.</p>
